WEBVTT

00:01:33.460 --> 00:01:34.860
[OVERDO]

00:01:35.250 --> 00:01:37.600
[Episode 12]

00:01:47.000 --> 00:01:48.400
It's raining so heavily.

00:01:48.870 --> 00:01:49.759
Let's go home.

00:01:49.920 --> 00:01:52.229
My wife and kids are waiting for me at home.

00:01:52.229 --> 00:01:53.950
Let's go home.

00:01:56.160 --> 00:01:59.990
[Mingguang Grand Theater]

00:02:00.760 --> 00:02:02.160
Where on earth did you go?

00:02:11.750 --> 00:02:12.800
Murong Qingyi,

00:02:14.870 --> 00:02:17.280
What kind of life did you live before?

00:02:27.310 --> 00:02:29.000
You are a member of the Murong family.

00:02:29.000 --> 00:02:32.200
You don't have to be ordered around by others all the time.

00:02:33.310 --> 00:02:34.590
What if I don't apologize?

00:02:34.590 --> 00:02:35.430
Are you going to kill me today?

00:02:35.430 --> 00:02:36.680
How many times have you targeted your sister-in-law?

00:02:36.680 --> 00:02:37.520
Everyone else is innocent.

00:02:37.520 --> 00:02:38.590
I'm the only bad seed,

00:02:38.590 --> 00:02:41.050
The disgrace of the Murong family, alright?

00:02:50.340 --> 00:02:51.000
Susu,

00:02:51.670 --> 00:02:54.280
No one in this world understands you better than I do.

00:02:54.280 --> 00:02:55.470
I'll say it again.

00:02:57.000 --> 00:02:58.600
Don't meddle in my business.

00:03:04.800 --> 00:03:06.470
Since it's destined,

00:03:07.800 --> 00:03:09.710
Why should we struggle?

00:03:11.590 --> 00:03:12.630
Wontons!

00:03:14.840 --> 00:03:16.100
Have a bowl of wontons!

00:03:24.240 --> 00:03:24.840
Is it good?

00:03:27.400 --> 00:03:28.460
At a time like this,

00:03:28.680 --> 00:03:30.710
A bowl of hot soy milk would be great.

00:03:31.120 --> 00:03:33.320
But soy milk is only sold in the morning.

00:03:33.630 --> 00:03:35.310
I'll take you to Nancheng someday.

00:03:35.310 --> 00:03:38.030
There's a late-night snack stall there where you can buy soy milk.

00:03:38.030 --> 00:03:40.360
My mom used to take me there when I was a kid.

00:03:40.470 --> 00:03:42.430
Do you take your mom there now?

00:04:07.190 --> 00:04:08.310
Here comes the soy milk.

00:04:08.310 --> 00:04:09.710
Drink slowly. It's hot.

00:04:14.240 --> 00:04:15.310
Qingyi.

00:04:22.200 --> 00:04:25.690
[Zeng Yinqiu, Li Rongzhang's Wife]

00:04:32.600 --> 00:04:34.000
I seem to have forgotten.

00:04:34.159 --> 00:04:36.290
You don't know how to use it yet, do you?

00:04:39.120 --> 00:04:41.600
I can just drink it from the bowl.

00:05:11.830 --> 00:05:12.760
Why are you here?

00:05:17.680 --> 00:05:20.080
Li Rongzhang just came and made a big scene,

00:05:20.800 --> 00:05:23.560
Saying that the Huo family had severed the tendons in your hand in prison.

00:05:23.560 --> 00:05:24.920
He demanded the Murong family

00:05:24.920 --> 00:05:27.780
Compensate him with 200 boxes of rifle ammunition.

00:05:28.070 --> 00:05:29.120
That old fox.

00:05:30.510 --> 00:05:32.240
He never lets himself lose out.

00:05:33.070 --> 00:05:34.600
Why didn't you tell Qingyu?

00:05:38.360 --> 00:05:40.120
He forced me to confess

00:05:40.120 --> 00:05:41.320
And sent me to prison.

00:05:41.750 --> 00:05:42.880
Would he believe it?

00:05:44.920 --> 00:05:47.250
Back then, the Huo family was pushing hard

00:05:47.360 --> 00:05:48.600
And insisting on killing you.

00:05:48.600 --> 00:05:50.000
To save your life, Qingyu

00:05:51.360 --> 00:05:52.760
Used all his connections

00:05:53.480 --> 00:05:56.310
And had no choice but to send you to prison for 3 years.

00:05:56.310 --> 00:05:57.830
I just think it's ridiculous that you

00:05:57.830 --> 00:05:58.830
Couldn't clear up

00:05:59.240 --> 00:06:01.100
Such a simple misunderstanding.

00:06:02.240 --> 00:06:03.680
Did you come all the way here

00:06:03.680 --> 00:06:04.950
Just to make me mad?

00:06:09.240 --> 00:06:10.560
You told me before

00:06:11.560 --> 00:06:13.220
That when you're in a bad mood,

00:06:15.240 --> 00:06:17.100
You come to this shop for soy milk.

00:06:26.720 --> 00:06:27.360
So?

00:06:28.830 --> 00:06:29.680
Right at this moment,

00:06:29.680 --> 00:06:30.950
You have to cling to me.

00:06:32.240 --> 00:06:33.770
Seeing me look like a loser,

00:06:34.120 --> 00:06:34.830
Are you very happy?

00:06:34.830 --> 00:06:36.490
I never thought of it that way.

00:06:43.159 --> 00:06:44.560
I'm also responsible...

00:06:46.480 --> 00:06:47.540
For what happened.

00:06:47.750 --> 00:06:48.600
I know.

00:06:49.600 --> 00:06:51.800
You just want Qingyu to misunderstand.

00:06:53.270 --> 00:06:55.159
You want him to think that I am targeting you.

00:06:55.159 --> 00:06:55.920
This way,

00:06:56.270 --> 00:06:57.830
No matter what I say in the future,

00:06:57.830 --> 00:06:58.960
He won't believe it.

00:06:59.680 --> 00:07:00.270
Right?

00:07:00.630 --> 00:07:01.800
About the wedding dress,

00:07:01.800 --> 00:07:03.800
I was just trying to protect myself.

00:07:07.630 --> 00:07:09.490
But I'm talking about Huo Mingxi.

00:07:10.600 --> 00:07:12.120
If I hadn't killed him...

00:07:14.120 --> 00:07:16.050
-your hand... -No need to explain.

00:07:17.270 --> 00:07:17.920
I know.

00:07:20.040 --> 00:07:22.100
You were just doing what you had to do.

00:07:23.160 --> 00:07:23.800
And I

00:07:25.310 --> 00:07:26.070
Just happened to be

00:07:26.070 --> 00:07:27.670
The one you didn't consider.

00:07:29.240 --> 00:07:30.770
It was like this in the past,

00:07:32.510 --> 00:07:34.110
And it's still like this now.

00:07:42.159 --> 00:07:43.190
Your brother now

00:07:45.310 --> 00:07:46.480
Hates the Huo family to the core.

00:07:46.480 --> 00:07:47.810
Isn't that a good thing?

00:07:47.870 --> 00:07:49.510
You want to deal with the Huo family.

00:07:49.510 --> 00:07:50.800
This way, my brother

00:07:51.040 --> 00:07:52.370
Can become your weapon.

00:07:52.510 --> 00:07:55.110
You're really going to marry the right person.

00:07:57.310 --> 00:08:00.040
I got some information out of Li Rongzhang today.

00:08:00.120 --> 00:08:01.190
The Huo family's vault

00:08:01.190 --> 00:08:02.790
Probably has a huge problem.

00:08:03.360 --> 00:08:04.920
The Huo family does charity on the surface,

00:08:04.920 --> 00:08:06.920
But behind the scenes, it's all dirty business.

00:08:06.920 --> 00:08:08.750
They collect orphans from everywhere,

00:08:08.750 --> 00:08:10.720
Divide them into different classes,

00:08:10.720 --> 00:08:11.980
Sell them as laborers,

00:08:12.560 --> 00:08:13.750
Sell their organs,

00:08:14.070 --> 00:08:16.400
Or deliberately maim them so they can beg.

00:08:17.600 --> 00:08:18.800
Those with good looks

00:08:19.070 --> 00:08:21.070
Will be sent to a mysterious auction

00:08:21.120 --> 00:08:23.050
To be sold to the rich and powerful.

00:08:25.040 --> 00:08:26.240
This is the latest list

00:08:26.240 --> 00:08:28.190
Of missing girls from the orphanage.

00:08:28.190 --> 00:08:28.920
Perhaps

00:08:29.430 --> 00:08:30.480
You want to join me

00:08:30.480 --> 00:08:33.210
To seek revenge against the Huo family yourself.

00:08:33.909 --> 00:08:34.840
What do you mean?

00:08:39.360 --> 00:08:40.760
Whether you want to use me

00:08:41.480 --> 00:08:42.600
Or just pity me,

00:08:43.150 --> 00:08:44.610
I don't want to play along.

00:08:45.440 --> 00:08:46.000
And also,

00:08:46.840 --> 00:08:47.640
You shouldn't

00:08:47.870 --> 00:08:49.400
Come to this place anymore.

00:08:49.550 --> 00:08:51.010
It's not very suitable...

00:08:51.320 --> 00:08:53.380
For the young miss of the Fang family.

00:09:00.550 --> 00:09:02.480
Maybe it's right for him to do this.

00:09:03.870 --> 00:09:05.070
Staying away from me,

00:09:05.910 --> 00:09:07.750
Just as I always wanted.

00:09:09.040 --> 00:09:11.230
[Benevolence as the Foundation, Healing to Save the World]

00:09:15.840 --> 00:09:17.390
If I had never appeared,

00:09:18.320 --> 00:09:20.390
You could have had a better life.

00:09:36.320 --> 00:09:39.660
♪ Hate is the smoke left by dying flames ♪

00:09:40.000 --> 00:09:43.150
♪ Love is the warmth lingering after the wildfire ♪

00:09:41.390 --> 00:09:42.550
Thank you, Doctor.

00:09:43.620 --> 00:09:46.910
♪ Love and hate collide in a blaze ♪

00:09:44.150 --> 00:09:44.750
Don't mention it.

00:09:44.750 --> 00:09:45.200
Don't forget your medicine.

00:09:45.200 --> 00:09:45.800
Thank you.

00:09:47.550 --> 00:09:50.680
♪ Devour me all ♪

00:09:50.720 --> 00:09:54.020
♪ Ahead lies a tangle of joys and sorrows ♪

00:09:54.550 --> 00:09:57.860
♪ Behind remain the bitterness of unspoken feelings ♪

00:09:58.010 --> 00:10:01.530
♪ The heart races with every thought ♪

00:10:01.570 --> 00:10:04.730
♪ As long as we loved each other, I don't care ♪

00:10:04.830 --> 00:10:08.490
♪ Is it a blessing or a curse? ♪

00:10:10.390 --> 00:10:11.080
Susu,

00:10:10.910 --> 00:10:13.790
♪ If the sparks ♪

00:10:11.240 --> 00:10:12.240
Do you believe me?

00:10:12.630 --> 00:10:13.600
I will definitely

00:10:13.600 --> 00:10:15.200
Become the best surgeon.

00:10:13.820 --> 00:10:16.700
♪ Could fly back into the gun's muzzle ♪

00:10:19.020 --> 00:10:23.790
♪ If I had turned away when love first bloomed ♪

00:10:26.340 --> 00:10:32.090
♪ Perhaps I could've walked away unscathed ♪

00:10:34.080 --> 00:10:38.500
♪ Sadly, fate leaves no room for "if" ♪

00:10:52.510 --> 00:10:54.720
[Murong Residence]

00:11:06.270 --> 00:11:07.400
Where have you been?

00:11:09.440 --> 00:11:10.640
Even if I die outside,

00:11:11.000 --> 00:11:12.730
What does it have to do with you?

00:11:22.960 --> 00:11:24.090
You're an adult now!

00:11:25.200 --> 00:11:26.320
Disappearing whenever you want!

00:11:26.320 --> 00:11:27.030
Running away from home!

00:11:27.030 --> 00:11:28.390
Do you know there are people who are worried about you?

00:11:28.390 --> 00:11:29.030
Who?

00:11:29.510 --> 00:11:30.360
Cheng Jinzhi?

00:11:30.550 --> 00:11:31.550
Or Murong Jinrui?

00:11:31.550 --> 00:11:32.320
Or Li Rongzhang?

00:11:32.320 --> 00:11:33.030
Me!

00:11:34.000 --> 00:11:35.460
I looked for you all night!

00:11:38.200 --> 00:11:38.750
Fine.

00:11:39.720 --> 00:11:40.920
Then beat me to death.

00:11:42.670 --> 00:11:43.400
Come with me!

00:12:06.200 --> 00:12:07.080
I'm sorry.

00:12:07.480 --> 00:12:09.540
This gentleman was severely injured

00:12:09.550 --> 00:12:10.510
Back then.

00:12:10.670 --> 00:12:12.870
Although he has recovered now,

00:12:13.150 --> 00:12:15.000
He should still experience occasional

00:12:15.000 --> 00:12:17.480
Dull pain and spasms.

00:12:18.670 --> 00:12:20.480
Can't his hand fully recover?

00:12:20.670 --> 00:12:22.000
My brother is a surgeon.

00:12:22.030 --> 00:12:23.560
His hand cannot be damaged.

00:12:24.000 --> 00:12:24.840
His hand

00:12:25.240 --> 00:12:26.390
Can handle

00:12:26.670 --> 00:12:27.750
Daily life,

00:12:28.120 --> 00:12:29.840
But to recover

00:12:29.840 --> 00:12:32.110
To the precision required for surgery,

00:12:32.750 --> 00:12:33.630
I'm afraid

00:12:33.840 --> 00:12:35.240
There's nothing I can do.

00:12:35.510 --> 00:12:36.840
Is there no other way?

00:12:37.870 --> 00:12:38.960
I'm sorry.

00:12:39.320 --> 00:12:40.670
I told you it's pointless.

00:12:40.670 --> 00:12:41.270
It can't be restored.

00:12:41.270 --> 00:12:42.870
You insisted on coming here.

00:12:44.240 --> 00:12:45.370
Such a waste of time.

00:12:50.080 --> 00:12:51.080
Stop right there!

00:12:51.480 --> 00:12:52.480
I told you to stop!

00:12:55.510 --> 00:12:56.360
If this hospital doesn't work,

00:12:56.360 --> 00:12:57.620
We can try another one.

00:12:57.870 --> 00:13:00.390
I heard there's a good hospital in Hangcheng.

00:13:00.390 --> 00:13:01.120
We can try again there.

00:13:01.120 --> 00:13:02.720
Stop being so hypocritical.

00:13:03.000 --> 00:13:05.150
I don't need you to seek medical help for me.

00:13:05.150 --> 00:13:06.480
It's just a ruined hand.

00:13:06.870 --> 00:13:08.730
It just means I can't be a surgeon.

00:13:09.000 --> 00:13:11.200
I can still be the scapegoat for the Murong family.

00:13:11.200 --> 00:13:13.510
I can still be a stepping stone for you.

00:13:14.840 --> 00:13:16.100
It's not enough, is it?

00:13:16.360 --> 00:13:17.320
If it's not enough,

00:13:17.320 --> 00:13:18.910
You can ruin my right hand too.

00:13:18.910 --> 00:13:19.770
Is that enough?

00:13:32.600 --> 00:13:34.790
Serve Young Master Qingyi well.

00:13:35.630 --> 00:13:36.870
He's locked up here.

00:13:37.670 --> 00:13:38.960
It seems the Murong family

00:13:38.960 --> 00:13:40.240
Doesn't care about his life

00:13:40.240 --> 00:13:41.480
As an abandoned pawn.

00:14:02.000 --> 00:14:03.730
Murong Qingyu, remember this.

00:14:04.870 --> 00:14:06.960
You were the one who sent me to prison.

00:14:08.080 --> 00:14:10.410
Why are you acting like a good brother now?

00:14:11.270 --> 00:14:12.480
You are no different

00:14:13.270 --> 00:14:14.270
From Cheng Jinzhi

00:14:14.840 --> 00:14:15.840
And Li Rongzhang!

00:14:20.390 --> 00:14:21.670
I'm sorry!

00:14:29.630 --> 00:14:30.720
It was my fault.

00:14:36.550 --> 00:14:37.720
It was my fault.

00:14:41.150 --> 00:14:42.350
I remember back then,

00:14:44.600 --> 00:14:46.200
When you finally recovered,

00:14:48.030 --> 00:14:48.870
I asked you

00:14:49.750 --> 00:14:51.150
What you wanted to study.

00:14:53.270 --> 00:14:55.000
You told me without hesitation

00:14:55.910 --> 00:14:57.840
That you wanted to study medicine.

00:14:58.510 --> 00:14:59.510
So I

00:15:00.550 --> 00:15:02.120
Sent you to study abroad

00:15:03.030 --> 00:15:04.890
So you could study medicine well.

00:15:06.720 --> 00:15:08.380
You occasionally wrote to me.

00:15:09.030 --> 00:15:10.690
The contents of those letters

00:15:12.030 --> 00:15:13.960
Were all about medical knowledge.

00:15:18.000 --> 00:15:19.440
Actually, at that time,

00:15:22.320 --> 00:15:24.000
I was happy for you.

00:15:26.870 --> 00:15:28.330
I was really happy for you.

00:15:44.200 --> 00:15:46.260
You finally came back to this family.

00:15:49.200 --> 00:15:50.860
You didn't trust anyone else.

00:15:53.510 --> 00:15:54.960
You could only trust me.

00:16:13.270 --> 00:16:14.000
Enough.

00:16:15.440 --> 00:16:16.970
Stop being so sentimental.

00:16:24.030 --> 00:16:25.000
Actually,

00:16:27.960 --> 00:16:29.620
It doesn't hurt that much now.

00:16:34.030 --> 00:16:34.870
Now,

00:16:36.870 --> 00:16:38.440
What can I do for you

00:16:39.910 --> 00:16:41.270
To make you feel better?

00:16:42.720 --> 00:16:44.450
I will definitely satisfy you.

00:16:53.200 --> 00:16:54.600
There really is one thing

00:16:56.480 --> 00:16:57.480
You can do for me.

00:17:04.160 --> 00:17:05.560
Let me take another bite.

00:17:10.069 --> 00:17:12.790
-This illness is so scary when it flares up. -Get out!

00:17:12.790 --> 00:17:14.069
He is so young.

00:17:14.510 --> 00:17:15.720
-Young Master Qingyi... -Qingyi, don't be afraid.

00:17:15.720 --> 00:17:16.720
I'm your brother!

00:17:19.750 --> 00:17:20.550
Hang in there!

00:17:20.920 --> 00:17:22.000
You can do this!

00:18:25.930 --> 00:18:29.220
[Huo Residence]

00:18:34.240 --> 00:18:35.040
Young Master,

00:18:35.270 --> 00:18:37.070
A letter from the Murong family.

00:18:38.540 --> 00:18:40.890
[Letter of Annulment]

00:18:41.310 --> 00:18:42.510
Letter of annulment?

00:18:43.270 --> 00:18:44.160
Who sent it?

00:18:44.750 --> 00:18:46.160
That bastard Murong Qingyi?

00:18:46.160 --> 00:18:47.360
It was Murong Qingyu.

00:18:49.240 --> 00:18:50.640
We've already had the engagement ceremony.

00:18:50.170 --> 00:18:53.500
[I hereby announce that the engagement between my younger brother and Miss Minxian is dissolved.]

00:18:50.960 --> 00:18:53.400
He can't just cancel the engagement whenever he wants.

00:18:53.400 --> 00:18:55.480
Murong Qingyu also asked me to pass on a message.

00:18:55.480 --> 00:18:56.240
Tell me.

00:18:56.960 --> 00:18:57.720
What is it?

00:18:59.590 --> 00:19:00.450
What did he say?

00:19:01.680 --> 00:19:03.280
"The losses of the Huo family

00:19:03.790 --> 00:19:05.920
Are not enough to cover even a fraction of my brother's medical bills.

00:19:05.920 --> 00:19:07.090
If the Huo family can't accept it,

00:19:07.090 --> 00:19:07.760
[I hereby announce that the engagement between my younger brother and Miss Minxian is dissolved.]

00:19:07.400 --> 00:19:10.660
You can come to the Cheng Army and ask me for compensation."

00:19:17.150 --> 00:19:21.530
[Linglong Cheongsam]

00:19:21.590 --> 00:19:26.270
[Closed]

00:19:26.380 --> 00:19:27.930
[Nancheng Main Sewer System Map]

00:19:26.680 --> 00:19:27.510
A few days ago,

00:19:27.640 --> 00:19:29.900
I secretly investigated the Huo family.

00:19:30.160 --> 00:19:33.160
[Huo family] [Zhenhua Aviation School] [Church] [Xanadu Cabaret] [Dongjiadu]

00:19:30.440 --> 00:19:33.440
This is the route map for their goods transportation.

00:19:33.590 --> 00:19:35.000
I found female hair

00:19:35.160 --> 00:19:36.590
In one of the supply carts,

00:19:36.590 --> 00:19:38.720
As well as the lingering smell of sulfur soap.

00:19:38.720 --> 00:19:39.750
I remember the orphanage

00:19:39.750 --> 00:19:41.440
Has always used this kind of soap.

00:19:41.440 --> 00:19:42.350
So,

00:19:42.510 --> 00:19:43.640
These supply carts

00:19:43.720 --> 00:19:46.120
Were indeed used to transport these girls.

00:19:46.160 --> 00:19:48.270
But why transport them to Dongjiadu?

00:19:48.380 --> 00:19:48.930
[The Latest Map of Nancheng]

00:19:49.640 --> 00:19:52.680
Perhaps delivering supplies for charity to Dongjiadu

00:19:52.680 --> 00:19:54.610
Is a way for them to cover things up.

00:19:55.400 --> 00:19:57.680
But what method did they use

00:19:57.920 --> 00:19:59.920
To transfer the girls to another place

00:19:59.920 --> 00:20:01.160
After bringing them to Dongjiadu?

00:20:00.160 --> 00:20:01.150
[Church] [Xanadu Cabaret] [Dongjiadu]

00:20:01.180 --> 00:20:02.750
[Huo family] [Zhenhua Aviation School] [Mingguang Grand Theater]

00:20:01.510 --> 00:20:03.570
If they are trafficking these girls,

00:20:03.680 --> 00:20:04.940
They must have a venue.

00:20:05.070 --> 00:20:06.790
The most reasonable explanation is that

00:20:06.790 --> 00:20:08.070
Dongjiadu can directly lead to

00:20:08.070 --> 00:20:09.200
That trading venue.

00:20:11.440 --> 00:20:13.440
Where is the Huo family's Hong Fang Bank?

00:20:13.440 --> 00:20:16.000
You suspect Hong Fang Bank is the shipping location?

00:20:16.000 --> 00:20:17.200
How is that possible?

00:20:17.270 --> 00:20:18.480
Dongjiadu is a slum,

00:20:18.720 --> 00:20:21.270
While Hong Fang Bank is in the most prosperous wealthy area.

00:20:21.270 --> 00:20:23.400
Besides, Hong Fang Bank is the foundation of the Huo family,

00:20:21.550 --> 00:20:23.780
[Dongjiadu]

00:20:23.550 --> 00:20:25.000
Having operated legally for decades.

00:20:23.780 --> 00:20:26.410
[Hong Fang Bank]

00:20:25.880 --> 00:20:27.880
Would the Huo family really carry out

00:20:27.880 --> 00:20:29.240
Such a dirty business there?

00:20:29.240 --> 00:20:30.440
Both sides of Dongjiadu

00:20:29.590 --> 00:20:33.020
[Church] [Dongjiadu]

00:20:30.720 --> 00:20:32.430
Are ordinary residential areas.

00:20:32.430 --> 00:20:34.480
One side has the church and charity hospital.

00:20:33.060 --> 00:20:35.670
[Church] [Charity Hospital]

00:20:34.960 --> 00:20:35.790
The other side

00:20:36.000 --> 00:20:37.200
Is a ditch.

00:20:37.550 --> 00:20:39.010
There is nothing unusual.

00:20:42.680 --> 00:20:43.550
A ditch?

00:20:44.350 --> 00:20:45.150
What's wrong?

00:20:47.750 --> 00:20:49.080
Besides the street map,

00:20:49.240 --> 00:20:51.070
Do you have a map of the sewer lines in this area?

00:20:49.430 --> 00:20:51.990
[Ditch]

00:20:52.110 --> 00:20:53.420
[Church] [Xanadu Cabaret] [Dongjiadu]

00:20:53.440 --> 00:20:54.590
[Huo family] [Zhenhua Aviation School] [Mingguang Grand Theater]

00:20:55.270 --> 00:20:57.070
Dongjiadu and Andeya Road

00:20:57.200 --> 00:20:58.770
Are simply two different worlds.

00:20:58.770 --> 00:21:03.880
[Dongjiadu] [Ditch] [Hong Fang Bank]

00:20:58.830 --> 00:21:00.070
Who would have thought

00:21:00.070 --> 00:21:01.270
That they are only separated by

00:21:01.270 --> 00:21:03.350
This short ditch.

00:21:05.000 --> 00:21:06.790
So the girls from the orphanage,

00:21:06.790 --> 00:21:08.450
After arriving at Dongjiadu,

00:21:08.640 --> 00:21:10.700
Were transported through this sewer

00:21:11.350 --> 00:21:12.880
To Hong Fang Bank.

00:21:13.730 --> 00:21:15.190
[Hong Fang Bank]

00:21:27.510 --> 00:21:28.590
I've already asked someone

00:21:28.590 --> 00:21:30.510
To find the best doctor in the country

00:21:30.510 --> 00:21:32.640
To come to Nancheng to treat your hand.

00:21:32.640 --> 00:21:33.720
It's pointless.

00:21:34.000 --> 00:21:35.110
Why is it pointless?

00:21:35.110 --> 00:21:36.030
If it doesn't work here,

00:21:36.030 --> 00:21:37.070
We'll go abroad.

00:21:37.270 --> 00:21:38.240
You must get treated.

00:21:38.240 --> 00:21:39.440
You can go if you want,

00:21:39.640 --> 00:21:40.640
But I'm not going.

00:21:42.550 --> 00:21:45.070
I haven't wanted to be a surgeon for a long time.

00:21:45.070 --> 00:21:47.270
As for my hand, it's fine as it is.

00:21:47.750 --> 00:21:48.590
Stop fussing.

00:21:51.550 --> 00:21:53.010
Then what do you want to do?

00:21:56.160 --> 00:21:57.480
I want to see someone

00:21:58.200 --> 00:21:58.960
Lose to me.

00:22:00.160 --> 00:22:00.830
Who?

00:22:04.310 --> 00:22:05.840
Just someone from the past.

00:22:07.550 --> 00:22:08.880
I lost to her before.

00:22:09.310 --> 00:22:10.310
I can't accept it,

00:22:11.000 --> 00:22:11.920
So I want to win.

00:22:17.510 --> 00:22:18.160
Alright.

00:22:19.640 --> 00:22:21.970
It's good that you have such an obsession.

00:22:22.310 --> 00:22:23.970
Then win it back beautifully.

00:22:24.790 --> 00:22:26.030
But some things

00:22:26.480 --> 00:22:27.940
Are actually not worth it.

00:22:28.160 --> 00:22:29.560
Let it go when you should.

00:22:32.110 --> 00:22:33.790
Let it go when you should?

00:22:35.440 --> 00:22:36.480
Then can you...

00:22:37.270 --> 00:22:39.330
Just let things go whenever you want?

00:22:41.440 --> 00:22:43.040
For example, you and that...

00:22:43.640 --> 00:22:44.440
Ms. Ye.

00:22:45.440 --> 00:22:46.000
Can you?

00:22:50.440 --> 00:22:51.920
I was with Ye before.

00:22:52.510 --> 00:22:54.770
-Then why did you say... -But that's all.

00:22:55.000 --> 00:22:57.060
My engagement to Mulan won't change.

00:22:58.000 --> 00:22:59.530
That's all you need to know.

00:23:04.590 --> 00:23:06.550
Not marrying the woman you like

00:23:06.550 --> 00:23:07.920
And marrying Fang Mulan instead?

00:23:07.920 --> 00:23:09.850
I don't know what you are thinking.

00:23:13.200 --> 00:23:15.240
I met Miss Fang in Nanyang.

00:23:16.310 --> 00:23:17.510
Her father is like...

00:23:18.070 --> 00:23:19.240
A savior to me.

00:23:20.240 --> 00:23:22.790
The alliance between the Fang and Murong families

00:23:22.790 --> 00:23:24.830
Will take both sides to new heights.

00:23:25.960 --> 00:23:28.090
As the eldest son of the Murong family,

00:23:29.160 --> 00:23:30.690
I have my responsibilities

00:23:31.110 --> 00:23:31.910
And my duties.

00:23:34.790 --> 00:23:35.880
Do you know

00:23:36.200 --> 00:23:38.030
What kind of person Miss Fang is?

00:23:40.030 --> 00:23:41.680
If her hands are covered in blood,

00:23:41.680 --> 00:23:42.790
And she has a vicious heart,

00:23:42.790 --> 00:23:44.030
Calculating every step,

00:23:44.030 --> 00:23:45.490
Would you still marry her?

00:23:46.680 --> 00:23:49.080
Why are you putting it in such a serious way?

00:23:50.880 --> 00:23:51.550
Right.

00:23:53.160 --> 00:23:54.590
After all, Miss Ye

00:23:54.790 --> 00:23:56.750
Is simple-minded, physically strong,

00:23:56.750 --> 00:23:57.680
And straightforward.

00:23:57.680 --> 00:23:59.070
She's just a martial artist,

00:23:59.070 --> 00:24:02.330
-unfit to be a young madam. -Don't talk about her like that.

00:24:15.310 --> 00:24:16.710
I still have to remind you

00:24:18.030 --> 00:24:19.290
That, in some matters,

00:24:19.830 --> 00:24:20.960
You can fool others,

00:24:21.920 --> 00:24:23.320
But don't fool yourself.

00:24:27.350 --> 00:24:29.160
The Fang family is far away in Nanyang.

00:24:29.160 --> 00:24:31.720
There are many things about them that we can't find out.

00:24:31.720 --> 00:24:34.720
Even if you want to form a marriage alliance with the Fang family,

00:24:34.720 --> 00:24:36.200
You'd better be careful.

00:24:37.750 --> 00:24:38.950
For example, you must

00:24:39.480 --> 00:24:40.940
Know clearly in your heart

00:24:41.590 --> 00:24:43.790
What kind of person Miss Fang really is.

00:25:20.310 --> 00:25:21.310
-Who are you? -Go!

00:25:23.910 --> 00:25:26.400
[Zhenhua No. 1 Aviation School]

00:25:24.920 --> 00:25:25.550
Police.

00:25:26.960 --> 00:25:28.310
How could this happen?

00:25:28.310 --> 00:25:29.970
How long has she been missing?

00:25:30.440 --> 00:25:31.550
Still no clues?

00:25:31.750 --> 00:25:34.350
The basic information on the missing teacher.

00:25:35.790 --> 00:25:37.350
Her name is Ye Zhihong.

00:25:37.640 --> 00:25:38.750
She has delicate features,

00:25:38.750 --> 00:25:39.440
Short hair,

00:25:39.880 --> 00:25:40.960
And is tall.

00:25:41.440 --> 00:25:43.400
She is a teaching assistant at the aviation school.

00:25:43.400 --> 00:25:44.960
When she went missing last night,

00:25:44.960 --> 00:25:46.160
What was she wearing?

00:25:46.270 --> 00:25:46.920
Well...

00:25:47.820 --> 00:25:50.960
[Zhenhua No. 1 Aviation School]

00:25:48.070 --> 00:25:48.960
A beige shirt,

00:25:48.960 --> 00:25:49.820
Grey trousers,

00:25:50.240 --> 00:25:51.370
And a silver brooch.

00:25:52.110 --> 00:25:53.310
Young Master Murong?

00:25:54.030 --> 00:25:55.440
Even the Principal is here?

00:25:55.440 --> 00:25:57.510
How does the Principal know so much about Ms. Ye?

00:25:57.510 --> 00:25:58.070
Well...

00:25:58.070 --> 00:25:58.730
Principal,

00:25:58.920 --> 00:26:02.030
Our police station will definitely do its best to investigate.

00:26:02.030 --> 00:26:03.430
But don't worry too much.

00:26:03.550 --> 00:26:05.200
You must take care of yourself.

00:26:05.200 --> 00:26:06.110
Ms. Ye

00:26:06.110 --> 00:26:07.200
Is an adult.

00:26:07.400 --> 00:26:09.790
Maybe she had an emergency and went back to her hometown.

00:26:09.790 --> 00:26:10.720
She is an orphan.

00:26:10.790 --> 00:26:11.790
Her relatives in her hometown

00:26:11.790 --> 00:26:13.050
Didn't treat her well.

00:26:13.790 --> 00:26:15.190
I've never heard of them.

00:26:15.310 --> 00:26:16.030
Besides,

00:26:16.440 --> 00:26:18.300
She is a very responsible person.

00:26:18.310 --> 00:26:19.640
She would never do that.

00:26:20.750 --> 00:26:22.880
The missing person is a teacher from our aviation school.

00:26:22.880 --> 00:26:24.240
Judging from the current situation,

00:26:24.240 --> 00:26:26.510
Something unexpected must have happened.

00:26:26.510 --> 00:26:27.350
So please,

00:26:27.880 --> 00:26:28.750
Do your best.

00:26:28.750 --> 00:26:30.550
We will definitely do everything we can

00:26:30.550 --> 00:26:31.400
To find Ms. Ye.

00:26:34.400 --> 00:26:34.930
Let's go.

00:26:36.350 --> 00:26:37.550
Stop gathering around.

00:26:37.550 --> 00:26:45.360
[Zhenhua No. 1 Aviation School]

00:26:37.590 --> 00:26:38.520
Go back to class.

00:26:39.720 --> 00:26:41.050
Principal. Principal.

00:26:41.160 --> 00:26:43.070
I have dispatched our men to look for her.

00:26:43.070 --> 00:26:45.400
Her neighbors said Ms. Ye hadn't returned for a day

00:26:45.400 --> 00:26:48.070
And that nothing unusual had happened recently.

00:26:48.070 --> 00:26:50.270
We searched the place where Ms. Ye volunteered as a teacher,

00:26:50.270 --> 00:26:51.530
But we didn't find her.

00:26:53.400 --> 00:26:54.110
Keep searching.

00:26:54.110 --> 00:26:54.640
Yes.

00:26:54.980 --> 00:26:56.850
[Zhenhua No. 1 Aviation School]

00:26:55.920 --> 00:26:57.720
Principal, where are you going?

00:27:11.480 --> 00:27:12.070
Qingyu.

00:27:13.270 --> 00:27:14.200
Are you sure this is the route

00:27:14.200 --> 00:27:15.730
Ms. Ye must take to commute?

00:27:17.720 --> 00:27:18.830
You observed the footprints

00:27:18.830 --> 00:27:20.110
And studied the soil.

00:27:21.440 --> 00:27:22.640
And after all that,

00:27:22.920 --> 00:27:24.920
Inspector Li, you still need to ask?

00:27:25.550 --> 00:27:27.150
The traces are too messy now.

00:27:27.350 --> 00:27:27.920
Indeed,

00:27:28.240 --> 00:27:30.170
My skills still need improvement.

00:27:30.240 --> 00:27:31.700
If your skills are poor...

00:27:31.830 --> 00:27:33.110
This is indeed the route Ms. Ye

00:27:33.110 --> 00:27:35.310
Takes to the aviation school every day.

00:27:56.070 --> 00:27:57.000
Silver Hademen.

00:27:58.030 --> 00:28:00.360
It seems there was indeed a struggle here.

00:28:14.960 --> 00:28:15.720
-Go! -Go!

00:28:15.790 --> 00:28:16.270
Go!

00:28:17.240 --> 00:28:18.070
Who are you?

00:28:29.310 --> 00:28:30.350
These bushes

00:28:30.920 --> 00:28:32.320
Show signs of a struggle.

00:28:45.000 --> 00:28:45.680
Found it.

00:28:48.640 --> 00:28:49.400
This is it.

00:28:50.110 --> 00:28:51.200
This is the brooch

00:28:51.350 --> 00:28:52.880
Ms. Ye was wearing that day.

00:28:56.070 --> 00:28:57.070
Hong Fang Bank?

00:28:57.590 --> 00:28:58.720
It's the Huo family.

00:28:59.240 --> 00:29:01.400
The cigarette butt from earlier didn't have a tax stamp.

00:29:01.400 --> 00:29:02.480
It must have been smuggled out

00:29:02.480 --> 00:29:03.610
By factory workers.

00:29:03.640 --> 00:29:04.510
Give me some time.

00:29:04.510 --> 00:29:05.400
I can find these people.

00:29:05.400 --> 00:29:06.270
By the time you find them,

00:29:06.270 --> 00:29:08.670
Ms. Ye won't even have bone fragments left.

00:29:08.720 --> 00:29:09.310
Qingyu,

00:29:09.880 --> 00:29:11.070
Since we know it's the Huo family,

00:29:11.070 --> 00:29:13.440
We should just go and demand that they hand her over.

00:29:13.440 --> 00:29:14.640
Search thoroughly.

00:29:15.160 --> 00:29:16.230
It's best if the Huo family

00:29:16.230 --> 00:29:18.030
Hasn't had time to transfer her.

00:29:18.350 --> 00:29:20.030
-If we can't find her... -If we can't find her,

00:29:20.030 --> 00:29:21.490
I will make a bigger scene.

00:29:24.000 --> 00:29:25.260
We need to let them know

00:29:25.350 --> 00:29:26.480
That those who dare to lay a finger on my brother's woman

00:29:26.480 --> 00:29:27.720
Will pay the price.

00:29:32.470 --> 00:29:33.470
Causing trouble—

00:29:33.590 --> 00:29:34.390
I'm good at it.

00:29:43.640 --> 00:29:44.160
Qingyu.

00:29:44.790 --> 00:29:46.680
Do you need me to go back and call more people?

00:29:46.680 --> 00:29:47.920
With people from the police station there,

00:29:47.920 --> 00:29:49.980
The search will be more justifiable.

00:29:52.440 --> 00:29:53.500
Don't get involved

00:29:53.640 --> 00:29:54.510
In this for now.

00:29:57.100 --> 00:29:58.670
[Tung Teh Road]

00:29:58.700 --> 00:30:01.240
[Hong Fang Bank]

00:30:03.270 --> 00:30:03.790
Miss,

00:30:03.920 --> 00:30:04.850
We have arrived.

00:30:14.380 --> 00:30:17.500
[Hong Fang Bank]

00:30:26.640 --> 00:30:27.680
Hello, Madam.

00:30:27.680 --> 00:30:30.070
What kind of business would you like to handle?

00:30:30.070 --> 00:30:31.070
Asset custody.

00:30:34.720 --> 00:30:36.510
Then our Hong Fang Bank's custody services

00:30:36.510 --> 00:30:37.830
Are definitely your best choice.

00:30:37.070 --> 00:30:37.730
[Hong Fang Bank]

00:30:38.140 --> 00:30:39.200
[Hong Fang Bank]

00:30:42.270 --> 00:30:43.720
I'm not interested in

00:30:44.270 --> 00:30:45.870
Ordinary custody services.

00:30:47.550 --> 00:30:49.160
If it is convenient for you,

00:30:49.680 --> 00:30:51.350
Please step into our VIP room

00:30:51.480 --> 00:30:52.340
For a cup of tea.

00:30:52.790 --> 00:30:56.650
I will arrange for someone to introduce our business to you in detail.

00:30:58.160 --> 00:30:59.490
Madam, this way please.

00:31:06.400 --> 00:31:06.920
Please.

00:31:08.160 --> 00:31:08.750
Madam,

00:31:09.200 --> 00:31:10.130
This way please.

00:31:23.240 --> 00:31:24.270
May I have your last name?

00:31:24.270 --> 00:31:25.160
My last name is Wang.

00:31:25.160 --> 00:31:26.920
I am a property consultant dedicated to

00:31:26.920 --> 00:31:28.920
Serving our distinguished guests.

00:31:29.240 --> 00:31:31.170
Manager Wang, you're so thorough.

00:31:31.590 --> 00:31:32.830
No wonder Hong Fang Bank

00:31:32.830 --> 00:31:34.830
Can stand alongside Huaxi and Chada

00:31:35.070 --> 00:31:37.030
In a place like Nancheng,

00:31:37.030 --> 00:31:38.350
Where the strong gather.

00:31:38.350 --> 00:31:39.210
You flatter us.

00:31:39.440 --> 00:31:41.030
May I have your...

00:31:41.550 --> 00:31:42.680
My last name is Fang.

00:31:42.720 --> 00:31:43.720
I'm from Nanyang.

00:31:45.960 --> 00:31:47.030
Could you be...

00:31:47.030 --> 00:31:48.590
Miss Fang Mulan?

00:31:49.680 --> 00:31:50.550
You know me?

00:31:53.590 --> 00:31:55.110
For those of us in the financial industry,

00:31:55.110 --> 00:31:57.440
It is our duty to understand the global economic situation.

00:31:57.440 --> 00:31:58.350
The Fang family of Nanyang

00:31:58.350 --> 00:32:00.240
Has weathered many changes in Asia

00:32:00.240 --> 00:32:01.640
And still stands strong.

00:32:01.750 --> 00:32:03.240
We have naturally heard of your

00:32:03.240 --> 00:32:05.270
Strength and reputation.

00:32:06.400 --> 00:32:06.860
Come on.

00:32:11.830 --> 00:32:13.960
My elders want me to find a secure place

00:32:13.960 --> 00:32:14.590
To store

00:32:14.590 --> 00:32:16.640
These little things I brought.

00:32:17.920 --> 00:32:18.590
Miss Fang.

00:32:19.590 --> 00:32:21.110
Our bank has exclusive asset custody services

00:32:21.110 --> 00:32:23.350
For our distinguished guests.

00:32:24.240 --> 00:32:24.960
No one

00:32:25.240 --> 00:32:26.200
But our distinguished guests

00:32:26.200 --> 00:32:27.590
Can open this door.

00:32:27.960 --> 00:32:29.880
Behind the door is the secure area,

00:32:29.880 --> 00:32:32.470
Guarded by security 24 hours a day.

00:32:51.110 --> 00:32:52.440
These things of mine

00:32:53.000 --> 00:32:54.550
May not be very precious,

00:32:55.030 --> 00:32:56.440
But they were given to me by my elders

00:32:56.440 --> 00:32:58.350
As a dowry for my marriage far away from home.

00:32:58.350 --> 00:32:59.640
It's just that...

00:33:02.920 --> 00:33:04.580
Miss Fang, you must be joking.

00:33:04.920 --> 00:33:06.550
If you call these things small,

00:33:06.550 --> 00:33:09.880
I don't think there's anything valuable in all of Nancheng.

00:33:10.400 --> 00:33:12.110
It's just that apart from the jewelry,

00:33:12.110 --> 00:33:14.170
There are also antiques, paintings,

00:33:14.310 --> 00:33:15.770
Gold bars, and ornaments.

00:33:15.920 --> 00:33:17.720
They take up quite a bit of space.

00:33:18.070 --> 00:33:20.000
And there's a small amount of cash.

00:33:23.510 --> 00:33:25.310
Please rest assured, Miss Fang.

00:33:25.310 --> 00:33:27.510
Our bank also has an underground vault.

00:33:31.680 --> 00:33:33.240
Underground vault?

00:33:34.160 --> 00:33:35.750
Our bank's underground vault

00:33:35.750 --> 00:33:37.960
Is very famous in Nancheng.

00:33:38.200 --> 00:33:39.240
Let me put it this way,

00:33:39.240 --> 00:33:41.110
Even if the whole Nancheng is razed to the ground,

00:33:41.110 --> 00:33:42.970
As long as your things are with us,

00:33:43.030 --> 00:33:43.830
We can ensure

00:33:44.030 --> 00:33:45.890
That they will be perfectly safe.

00:33:47.920 --> 00:33:49.270
That sounds good.

00:33:49.550 --> 00:33:50.480
Take me to see it.

00:33:51.070 --> 00:33:51.800
Miss Fang...

00:33:53.030 --> 00:33:53.790
The vault

00:33:53.920 --> 00:33:54.960
Is heavily guarded,

00:33:54.960 --> 00:33:55.680
And entry and exit

00:33:55.680 --> 00:33:58.010
Are restricted to authorized staff only.

00:33:58.480 --> 00:33:59.340
Then forget it.

00:34:00.680 --> 00:34:01.720
Please forgive us, Miss Fang.

00:34:01.720 --> 00:34:02.640
We are doing this to protect

00:34:02.640 --> 00:34:03.970
Our clients' property.

00:34:05.240 --> 00:34:06.830
I'm storing my things with you,

00:34:06.830 --> 00:34:08.880
But I don't even know where they'll be kept.

00:34:08.880 --> 00:34:10.630
My father has taught me since I was young

00:34:10.630 --> 00:34:12.090
That seeing is believing.

00:34:13.550 --> 00:34:14.880
Miss Fang, please wait!

00:34:22.590 --> 00:34:23.480
Please wait.

00:34:23.960 --> 00:34:24.590
Miss Fang.

00:34:24.800 --> 00:34:25.710
The vault is a highly restricted area,

00:34:25.710 --> 00:34:27.630
So please wait here for a moment.

00:34:29.670 --> 00:34:30.199
Alright.

00:34:30.960 --> 00:34:31.420
Please.

00:34:45.630 --> 00:34:46.110
Please.

00:35:03.440 --> 00:35:04.040
Miss Fang,

00:35:04.230 --> 00:35:04.710
Please.

00:35:08.280 --> 00:35:09.230
The entire vault

00:35:09.320 --> 00:35:12.120
Is cast as a single reinforced concrete structure

00:35:12.190 --> 00:35:14.320
And reinforced with three 20-centimeter-thick

00:35:14.320 --> 00:35:15.320
Steel plates.

00:35:15.590 --> 00:35:17.520
This is the only entrance and exit.

00:35:17.670 --> 00:35:18.800
The password is known only to me

00:35:18.800 --> 00:35:20.920
And several directors of the Huo family.

00:35:20.920 --> 00:35:23.110
Each safe has its own independent password,

00:35:23.110 --> 00:35:23.800
Which is known

00:35:23.800 --> 00:35:25.600
Only to the clients themselves.

00:35:28.670 --> 00:35:29.510
Our clients

00:35:29.630 --> 00:35:31.480
Are prominent political and business figures,

00:35:31.480 --> 00:35:32.510
Socialites, and wealthy ladies from Nancheng,

00:35:32.510 --> 00:35:34.630
As well as some foreign merchants.

00:35:34.880 --> 00:35:36.810
They never use those foreign banks

00:35:36.880 --> 00:35:39.080
And only entrust their valuables to us.

00:35:39.590 --> 00:35:42.280
The walls of the entire vault are lined with soft protective materials,

00:35:42.280 --> 00:35:43.410
All for one purpose:

00:35:43.630 --> 00:35:46.550
To guarantee the safety of our clients' property.

00:35:47.710 --> 00:35:48.670
Miss Fang.

00:35:48.840 --> 00:35:49.670
Miss Fang.

00:35:49.960 --> 00:35:51.360
You can't go any further.

00:35:53.800 --> 00:35:55.200
How's the humidity here?

00:35:55.480 --> 00:35:57.280
Can my paintings be stored here?

00:35:58.230 --> 00:35:58.830
Miss Fang,

00:35:59.000 --> 00:35:59.670
Look here.

00:36:00.960 --> 00:36:01.480
Here,

00:36:02.280 --> 00:36:03.070
That corner,

00:36:03.320 --> 00:36:04.280
And this corner.

00:36:05.280 --> 00:36:06.280
The entire vault is equipped

00:36:06.280 --> 00:36:08.410
With an adequate ventilation system.

00:36:09.710 --> 00:36:10.440
Miss Fang.

00:36:10.960 --> 00:36:12.160
Any other questions?

00:36:14.440 --> 00:36:14.960
Please.

